column2: "Hey partner, remember when you asked me about what happened ten years ago?"
"Have you asked anyone else about that?"
"You haven't? That's okay. I doubt you would hear anything even if you did."
"I don't think you'll hear anything besides \"There was a battle with Dark Falz ten years ago\"."
"It doesn't seem like anyone remembers exactly what happened ten years ago."
"I even went and tried to research what happened on my own, but everything was classified."
"I don't know how they did it, but it seems that all of the facts have been hidden."
"Even so, that doesn't seem to explain why no one remembers my sister...."
"I don't know anything more than what I mentioned to you before."
"All I can say is that that's the one thing I won't let myself forget."
